transcription.summary: There is an issue with SourceWale where it incorrectly marks a person as added by one recruiter when they were actually added by another. The correct setting needs to be adjusted in SourceWale. A survey can be created through PCR, but it must be sent to people who are already in the database and cannot be sent to random people. It may be better to create a hidden webpage on the company website where people can fill out the survey and then notify via email when completed.
